## ğŸš€ Installation (Users)

1. Download ZIP from GitHub  
2. Go to `chrome://extensions`  
3. Enable **Developer Mode**  
4. Click **Load Unpacked**  
5. Select the project folder  
6. Pin the extension for fast access  

---

## ğŸ’¡ Usage

1. Open any Terms & Conditions or Privacy Policy page  
2. Click the extension  
3. Press **Summarize Terms & Conditions**  
4. View:
   - AI summary  
   - Confidence score  

---

## âš™ï¸ Development Setup (For Developers)

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Adityajk07/toc-ai-summarizer-extension.git
cd toc-ai-summarizer-extension
2. Install frontend dependencies
bash
Copy code
npm install
3. Install backend dependencies
bash
Copy code
cd local_proxy
npm install
4. Create .env inside local_proxy/
ini
Copy code
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key_here
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
PORT=3000
You can obtain your Gemini API key from Google AI Studio.
Copy it into .env using the format above.

5. Start build watchers
Tailwind:

bash
Copy code
npm run watch:css
Webpack/React:

bash
Copy code
npm run watch
6. Start the local proxy server
bash
Copy code
cd local_proxy
node server.js
7. Reload the extension via chrome://extensions
âš ï¸ Important Note About OpenAI Verification
