âœ”ï¸ Use V1, which relies solely on Gemini
âœ”ï¸ V1 requires only a Gemini API key
âœ”ï¸ V1 is available in the previous commit

V1 is ideal for:

Students

Free-tier users

Anyone without OpenAI API access

